		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'd been thinking: from there, when you add a player character, you can have it collide with those with less than ten cycles (check sprite-0 hit per-frame). And you can have the collision be pixel-perfect, not shaped like the displayed character, however you like.

		

